OL,6,FGranada Reports journalist Paul Crone
OL,7,Fwent to meet the campaigners to hear
OL,8,Fmore.
OL,10,FA campaign has been launched to
OL,11,Frestore the memorial of a captain from
OL,12,FWorld War One.
OL,14,FCaptain Houston Stewart Hamilton
OL,15,FWallace from Birkenhead was killed in
OL,16,FFrance on 22 July 1916 in Northern
OL,17,FFrance but his body was never found.
OL,19,FHis aunt arranged for a private
OL,20,Fmemorial.
