OL,3,CMission underway to restore hero's WW1
OL,4,Cmemorial
OL,6,FShe cared for it alongside the
OL,7,FCommonwealth War Graves Commission
OL,8,F(CWGC) maintained it for 20 years.
OL,10,FA project is now underway on the
OL,11,FWirral to improve the memorial near
OL,12,Fwhere he died in Bazentin on the Somme.
OL,14,FThe campaigners want to restore the
OL,15,Fmemorial back to a pristine condition
OL,16,Fincluding a new plaque and making it
OL,17,Fmore accessible to visitors.
OL,19,FCaptain Wallace served with the 10th
OL,20,Fbattalion Worcestershire Regiment and
OL,21,Fwent to France on 1 August 1915.
