OL,4,Cmemorial
OL,6,FBoth his parents, William Hamilton and
OL,7,FEmily Constance, had died before he
OL,8,Fwent abroad and are buried in
OL,9,FFlaybrick Memorial Gardens in
OL,10,FBirkenhead.
OL,12,FCaptain Wallace's name can not be
OL,13,Ffound on the walls of the famous
OL,14,FThiepval Memorial in Northern France
OL,15,Fbut it is on the Calvary at Bazentin
OL,16,Fnear where he lost his life.
OL,18,FHe died after an unsuccessful mission
OL,19,Fto capture a German machine gun post.
OL,21,FA has been started to raise #5500.
